        "paragraph_index": 3,
        "text": "### 📌 Interpretation\n\n**SRD-46 does not include uranium(VI)/UO₂²⁺ as a metal entity**, and therefore no stability constants for uranyl–crown ether complexes are catalogued in this database. The crown ether data in SRD-46 is focused on alkali metals (Na⁺, K⁺, Cs⁺, Rb⁺), alkaline earths (Ca²⁺, Sr²⁺, Ba²⁺, Ra²⁺), and a few transition/heavy metals (Ag⁺, Hg²⁺, Pb²⁺, Tl⁺).",
